    "en": {
      "title": "Trial at Bar for Black Monday: Speaker's request",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena has demanded that a three-judge Trial at Bar session be convened to investigate the Black Monday incident on Monday and the assassination of former parliamentarian Amarakeerthi Athukora.",
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena has made this request in response to a request made by Members of Parliament.",
        "A motion of condolence over the assassination of Amarakeerthi Athukorala was recently tabled in Parliament.",
        "Most of the members who attended and addressed it. It is noteworthy that a trial adjournment has been appointed in connection with the murder and an inquiry has been requested.",
        "Meanwhile, a 41-year-old suspect from the Nittambuwa area has been arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department in connection with the murder of Amarakeerthi MP in the Nittambuwa area."
      ],
